  ('Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift', 'single-leg-romanian-deadlift-kicking', 'Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift uses hip hinge, hip extension, foot tripod control to improve a key kicking-athlete problem: Builds posterior-chain strength and single-leg balance so the stance leg can hold posture while the kicking leg swings or recoils.', 'BEGINNER', 8, 3, 4, 45, 90, 135, 'Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift is a Capacity exercise for kicking athletes that trains single-leg hinge strength with direct carryover to plant-leg stability, kick recoil control, soccer follow-through control.', 'Primary subrole: hinge_posterior_chain_strength. Coach this as Capacity work: preserve the intended phase, dose the drill by quality, and connect every rep to support-leg control, hip action, trunk transfer, and safe reset behavior.', 'Reach long, keep the hip square, pull back to tall.', 'Single-leg hinge strength', 'capacity', 'hinge_posterior_chain_strength', 'single_leg_rdl_kicking_posterior_chain', '{"primary_joint_actions":["hip hinge","hip extension","foot tripod control"],"primary_tissues":["hamstrings","glutes","calves"],"primary_motor_control_demands":[],"postural_shape":null,"breathing_demand":"medium","balance_demand":"high","coordination_demand":"medium","impact_level":0}'::jsonb, '{"movement_description":"Perform Single-Leg Romanian Deadlift with attention to hip hinge, hip extension, foot tripod control, then reset into a stance or position that would allow another kick, strike, or ball action.","setup":["Set up with dumbbells, kettlebell and enough open space for the athlete to move, pivot, and stop without crowding.","Explain the intended phase and quality gate before the first rep so the athlete knows whether this is access, skill, output, strength, resilience, conditioning, or restore work.","Establish stance foot pressure, rib-pelvis position, and a safe return/reset position before adding speed, load, target, or partner input.","Connect the drill to plant-leg stability, kick rec