  ('Eccentric Adductor Slider', 'eccentric-adductor-slider', 'Eccentric Adductor Slider uses hip abduction eccentric, hip adduction return, pelvic control to improve a key kicking-athlete problem: Progressively loads the groin in the lengthening direction that matters for high kicks, side reaches, ball striking, and lateral recovery.', 'BEGINNER', 8, 2, 4, 40, 45, 85, 'Eccentric Adductor Slider is a Resilience exercise for kicking athletes that trains adductor eccentric resilience with direct carryover to groin durability, high kick tolerance, soccer change of direction.', 'Primary subrole: slow_eccentric_isometric_joint_resilience. Coach this as Resilience work: preserve the intended phase, dose the drill by quality, and connect every rep to support-leg control, hip action, trunk transfer, and safe reset behavior.', 'Slide out slowly and pull back without yanking.', 'Adductor eccentric resilience', 'resilience', 'slow_eccentric_isometric_joint_resilience', 'eccentric_adductor_slider_kicking_resilience', '{"primary_joint_actions":["hip abduction eccentric","hip adduction return","pelvic control"],"primary_tissues":["adductors","groin connective tissue","obliques"],"primary_motor_control_demands":[],"postural_shape":null,"breathing_demand":"low","balance_demand":"medium","coordination_demand":"medium","impact_level":0}'::jsonb, '{"movement_description":"Perform Eccentric Adductor Slider with attention to hip abduction eccentric, hip adduction return, pelvic control, then reset into a stance or position that would allow another kick, strike, or ball action.","setup":["Set up with slider, mat and enough open space for the athlete to move, pivot, and stop without crowding.","Explain the intended phase and quality gate before the first rep so the athlete knows whether this is access, skill, output, strength, resilience, conditioning, or restore work.","Establish stance foot pressure, rib-pelvis position, and a safe return/reset position before adding speed, load, target,